br />\nVista200"},{"pid":"8028792e07283b0e040ff3e358c2da64f6f2ba84","tid":146602,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"正常好難斷，會唔會機入面有嘢爛咗變利，界斷片？"},{"pid":"598a07ef69d33587eafbf1ae55bc4fd29c5924e9","tid":146602,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常好難斷，會唔會機入面有嘢爛咗變利，界斷片？</blockquote><br />\n呢個真係唔清楚 番去睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8f18cb5b3adf60e04865c065a8817bd66d6bf6","tid":146602,"uid":30132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"係咪回片手法錯左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我都試過斷左兩次<br />\n回片之前要撳個底嗰粒制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b0933ffe7f3929eb96afd2b22c1aea59c8e043","tid":146602,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪回片手法錯左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我都試過斷左兩次<br />\n回片之前要撳個底嗰粒制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有撳 但好似撳完冇凹入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9ef7575e3d1976c75480a4cee12706c9d5e45f","tid":146602,"uid":14535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪回片手法錯左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我都試過斷左兩次<br />\n回片之前要撳個底嗰粒制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有撳 但好似撳完冇凹入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩機？有啲機要撳實回卷"},{"pid":"087fe695317aac2f4bc0466b986e2adb00d48f4b","tid":146602,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪回片手法錯左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我都試過斷左兩次<br />\n回片之前要撳個底嗰粒制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有撳 但好似撳完冇凹入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩機？有啲機要撳實回卷</blockquote><br />\nFujica st605"},{"pid":"dc3eb7724f5a05292b4a2da9e4afd7a5f8541f5b","tid":146602,"uid":14535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"同埋知唔知幾時斷？<br />\n其實過片會feel到有無上到菲林 過片會實啲<br />\n然後過片會見到回圈粒制會轉 多啲留意下有無轉 知道下幾時斷先判斷到點解會斷<br />\n有啲人就可能用自卷菲林但卷唔足 以為仲有片大力過扯斷<br />\n又有可能某隻菲林片基套薄過斷<br />\n又或者自己唔識用部機回卷卷斷<br />\n<br />\n如果回卷時斷其實feel到 本身好實 你出力 一出力轉就變到好鬆 = 斷左<br />\n本身好實 轉郁左 feel到正常有拖住菲林個種阻力 但半路放手會彈留轉頭 = 無按到回片粒制 搞到菲林上下卡住齒輪啲洞爛哂 （我曾經用Lomo LC- Wide 試過，但覺得唔對路問朋友覺個個回卷制要長按）"}]}